          <td colspan="2" valign="top" class="titulo2">Extract from &#8220;Borges: A Life&#8221; (2004) with a foreword (2008) and afterword (2008) <span class="texto2">by <a href="../../issue4/edwin_williamson/bio.php" class="link3">Edwin Williamson</a></span></td>
